title: Winter Walk
description:
Our story tonight is called “Winter Walk” and it’s a story about stepping through crisp layers of deep snow on a sunny cold day. It’s also about a well made bed, a sleeping kitty and the welcome way that nature can take your breath away.

So get cozy and ready to sleep.

Order the book now! hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens

Get our ad-free and bonus episodes here: https://nothingmuchhappens.supportingcast.fm
